<%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="container"
        style="max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
        </p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Information We Collect
        </h2>
        <p>When you register to use our platform, we collect information including your name, email address (via Google
            OAuth authentication), and details to complete purchases securely through payment processors (Razorpay,
            PayU).</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Security & Payments
        </h2>
        <p>Gurubrahma never directly stores your credit card information. Payments are strictly handled tokenized
            through third-party banking integration. Our database infrastructure is professionally managed and encrypted
            at rest.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or distribute your email or booking history to marketing agencies. Booking details are
            only shared between the specific user and the host selected for the 1:1 session so the calendar invites can
            be properly attached.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You reserve the right to request an extract of all data Gurubrahma has associated with your profile, or
            request immediate permanent deletion according to Indian regulatory standards and GDPR where applicable.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Contact Privacy Officer
        </h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or have a data request, please send an email. </p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@gurubrahma.online"
                style="color: #4f46e5;">support@gurubrahma.online</a></p>
        <p><strong>Offline Address:</strong><br>
            T-Hub Foundation,<br>
            1/C, 83/1, Raidurgam panmaktha,<br>
            Hyderabad Knowledge City, SERILINGAMPALLY,<br>
            Hyderabad, Telangana 500081, India
        </p>

    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>